{"vv14:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv14:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv14:0.3":"Pithavagga ","vv14:0.4":"14. Dutiyasunisavimanavatthu ","vv14:1.1":"“Abhikkantena vannena, ","vv14:1.2":"ya tvam titthasi devate; ","vv14:1.3":"Obhasenti disa sabba, ","vv14:1.4":"osadhi viya taraka. ","vv14:2.1":"Kena tetadiso vanno, ","vv14:2.2":"kena te idha mijjhati; ","vv14:2.3":"Uppajjanti ca te bhoga, ","vv14:2.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv14:3.1":"Pucchami tam devi mahanubhave, ","vv14:3.2":"Manussabhuta kimakasi punnam; ","vv14:3.3":"Kenasi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv14:3.4":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv14:4.1":"Sa devata attamana, ","vv14:4.2":"moggallanena pucchita; ","vv14:4.3":"Panham puttha viyakasi, ","vv14:4.4":"yassa kammassidam phalam. ","vv14:5.1":"“Aham manussesu manussabhuta, ","vv14:5.2":"Sunisa ahosim sasurassa gehe. ","vv14:6.1":"Addasam virajam bhikkhum, ","vv14:6.2":"vippasannamanavilam; ","vv14:6.3":"Tassa adasaham bhagam, ","vv14:6.4":"pasanna sehi panibhi; ","vv14:6.5":"Kummasapindam datvana, ","vv14:6.6":"modami nandane vane. ","vv14:7.1":"Tena metadiso vanno, ","vv14:7.2":"tena me idha mijjhati; ","vv14:7.3":"Uppajjanti ca me bhoga, ","vv14:7.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv14:8.1":"Akkhami te bhikkhu mahanubhava, ","vv14:8.2":"Manussabhuta yamakasi punnam; ","vv14:8.3":"Tenamhi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv14:8.4":"Vanno ca me sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv14:9.1":"Dutiyasunisavimanam cuddasamam. "}